15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 6-101.23, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 6-101.23. A. The dismissal, suspension and
19 nonreemployment provisions of the Teacher Due Process Act of 1990
20 shall not apply to:
21 1. Substitute teachers;
22 2. Adult education teachers; and
23 3. Teachers who are employed on temporary contracts.
24
